979_35-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFGimaret1979">Gimaret 1979</a>.</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEMartin199790-36"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEMartin199790_36-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFMartin1997">Martin 1997</a>, p.&#160;90.</span></li>\n<li id="cite_note-Kadri-118-37"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Kadri-118_37-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation book">Kadri, Sadakat (2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=ztCRZOhJ10wC&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;dq=Heaven+on+Earth:+A+Journey+Through+Shari%27a+Law&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=0CC0Q6AEwAWoVChMIob7syrnZxwIVhg6SCh0fYg3Z#v=onepage&amp;q=Heaven%20on%20Earth%3A%20A%20Journey%20Through%20Shari\'a%20Law&amp;f=false"><i>Heaven on Earth: A Journey Through Shari\'a Law from the Deserts of Ancient Arabia ...</i></a> macmillan. pp.&#160;118\xe2\x80\x939. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780099523277" title="Special:BookSources/9780099523277">9780099523277</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMu%CA%BFtazila&amp;rft.aufirst=Sadakat&amp;rft.aulast=Kadri&amp;rft.btitle=Heaven+on+Earth%3A+A+Journey+Through+Shari%27a+Law+from+the+Deserts+of+Ancient+Arabia+...&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9780099523277&amp;rft.pages=118-9&amp;rft.pub=macmillan&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DztCRZOhJ10wC%26printsec%3Dfrontcover%26dq%3DHeaven%2Bon%2BEarth%3A%2BA%2BJourney%2BThrough%2BShari%2527a%2BLaw%26hl%3Den%26sa%3DX%26ved%3D0CC0Q6AEwAWoVChMIob7syrnZxwIVhg6SCh0fYg3Z%23v%3Donepage%26q%3DHeaven%2520on%2520Earth%253A%2520A%2520Journey%2520Through%2520Shari%27a%2520Law%26f%3Dfalse&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook"